<section id="about">
<h2>About BLOSK</h2>
<p>BLOSK is a next generation platform where creators can shape anything, make anything using presets, and design interactive worlds for players. Users can explore and play these worlds, while creators have complete control over their environment.</p>
<p>Future updates will include collaboration features that allow multiple creators to work together and support for uploading custom models, expanding what is possible on the platform. BLOSK is a space where imagination meets capability and creativity drives the experience.</p>
</section>

